==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pannel
<hw>Pan"nel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Panel</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A kind of rustic saddle.</def>
<rj><au>Tusser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Falconry)</fld> <def>The stomach of a hawk.</def>
<rj><au>Ainsworth.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>A carriage for conveying a mortar
and its bed, on a march.</def> <rj><au>Farrow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pannier</ent>⟦br⟧
